flowchart TD
    Start((Start)) --> UserClick[User Clicks 'Update']
    UserClick --> CheckInternet{Internet Available?}
    
    CheckInternet -- No --> ShowError[Show Error Message]
    CheckInternet -- Yes --> RequestAPI[Request Weather API]
    
    RequestAPI --> Validate{Data Valid?}
    
    Validate -- No --> ShowError
    Validate -- Yes --> ProcessData[Process JSON Data]
    
    ProcessData --> UpdateState[Update Application State]
    UpdateState --> RenderUI[Re-render UI Components]
    
    ShowError --> Stop((End))
    RenderUI --> Stop